data.description: Charming turn of the Century bungalow in historic district features large front porch, original wood floors throughout main level, spacious eat-in kitchen with white cabinets, gas range, dishwasher, refrigerator, counter bar which sees into living room, new interior paint throughout, tall dual-pane vinyl windows for plenty of natural light, updated bathroom, new water heater, new ceiling fans,  laundry room off kitchen, new steel planter beds, privacy fence front and rear, spacious backyard with alley access and large storage shed/workshop.  Great location...walking distance to restaurants, Switchbacks stadium and downtown. Quick access to South Nevada Creek walk and nearby Monument Valley trail.  Click on both virtual tour links to see more!
